<fed2-map title='Link' version='43' editor='standard' from='2527' to='Asylum.Asylum Space.2015'>

   <location num='0' flags='t'>
      <name>Warehouse</name>
      <desc>This is where evil medical devices and unimplemented schemes are stored. However, you&apos;ll never see it, because it is totally inaccessible! MWAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!</desc>
      <desc>There are no exits to this room, and it&apos;s supposed to be a no teleport room. That means that if you&apos;re here and you&apos;re reading this, you&apos;ve fallen into a bug. Contact the staff for help.</desc>
   </location>

   <location num='287' flags='t'>
      <name>Hall of Memories</name>
      <desc>Even Firemonkeys have regrets. This dim, somber room is filled with small busts and statues of old friends of Monodefuego who shuffled off this mortal coil before he ever had the opportunity to enslave them and force them to do his will. They are the old friends long gone and the fish that got away all rolled into one, depressing package for the dictator. Here he has a memorial dedicated to them.</desc>
      <desc>Sleeperagent</desc>
      <desc>DarkAngel</desc>
      <desc>Pianoman</desc>
      <desc>Ferrerri</desc>
      <desc>I shall dominate you all in my dreams.</desc>
      <desc>The exit is out.</desc>
      <exits in='671' out='2401' no-exit='noexit.secret.5'/>
   </location>

